(42, 8, 23, 19, 44, 23, 23, NULL, 'Divine Wakefulness in Crisis', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine wakefulness during perilous situations. In both passages, the notion of sleep signifies a perceived absence of divine intervention amidst distress.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
